it should look something like this

&gt; configurations.all {
&gt;     resolutionStrategy {
&gt;         force 'com.squareup:javawriter:2.2.1’
&gt;    }
&gt; }

something like this would break it 

```
sourceSets {
    androidTest.java.srcDir 'src/test/java'
}
```

make a folder `src/unit_tests/java`

add this to your build 

```
android {
    sourceSets {
        test.java.srcDir 'src/unit_tests/java'
        }
}
```

Move your test there and try to run it

